{"lemma":"قَرُّ","slug":"قَرُّ","root":"ق.ر.ر","root_slug":"ق-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ر-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n35344","n35345","n35346"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become cold, to be cool, to be chilly"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to settle down, to linger, to remain"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to reside, to stay, to live (someone)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become established"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"cool, cold, chilly"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of قَرَّ (qarra, “to be cold”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"coldness, cold"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cold, coolness, coldness, chilliness, frigidity"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ق ر ر (q r r). Compare Hebrew קַר (qar, “cold”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35344","headword_ar":"قَرٌّ","root":"qr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1, throughout. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomu Alqar~i","text_ar":"يَوْمُ القَرِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The day of resting;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the eleventh day of Dhu-l-Hijjeh;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the first of the days called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ay~aAmu","text_ar":"اَيَّامُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~a$oriyqi","text_ar":"التَّشْرِيقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the day next after that called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomu Aln~aHori","text_ar":"يَوْمُ النَّحْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the day of the sacrifice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the slaughtering of camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, M, Mgh, K:) so called because the people on that day rest, or settle, in their abodes: (S, M, Mgh:) or because they rest on that day in [the valley of] Minè, (A 'Obeyd, Kr, M, Msb, K,) after the fatigue of the three days immediately preceding. (A 'Obeyd.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN qar~N","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ قَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) the inf. n. being thus used as an epithet, (Msb,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAr~N","text_ar":"قَارٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb,) but the latter was disapproved by IAar, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqoruwrN","text_ar":"مَقْرُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN qar~apN","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ قَرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAr~apN","text_ar":"قَارَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cold chill,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cool, day,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, &c.:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qar~N","text_ar":"قَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to anything as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cold;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) [and so, app., ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAr~N","text_ar":"قَارٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and perhaps ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaruwrN","text_ar":"قَرُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qariyrN","text_ar":"قَرِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqar~ataAni","text_ar":"القَرَّتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The two cold times;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the morning and the evening."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) A man being asked what had caused his teeth to fall out, he answered ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akolu AlHaAr~i wa$urobu AlqaAr~i","text_ar":"اَكْلُ الحَارِّ وَشُرْبُ القَارِّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eating what was hot, and drinking what was cold:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but he may have used"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAr~","text_ar":"قَارّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qr~","text_ar":"قرّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for the purpose of assimilation to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HAr~","text_ar":"حارّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and it seems that, when coupled or connected with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAr~N","text_ar":"حَارٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAr~N","text_ar":"قَارٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is more chaste than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qar~N","text_ar":"قَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) Respecting the saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wal~i HaAr~ahaA mano tawal~aY qaAr~ahaA","text_ar":"وَلِّ حَارَّهَا مَنْ تَوَلَّى قَارَّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hr","text_ar":"حر"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qur~N","text_ar":"قُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","M","Mgh","K","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n35345","headword_ar":"قُرٌّ","root":"qr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraArN","text_ar":"قَرَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] (S, M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotaqar~N","text_ar":"مُسْتَقَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqar~N","text_ar":"مَقَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"].       -A2-  Also, (S, M, Mgh, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qar~N","text_ar":"قَرٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lh, Kt,) which latter form, it is said, must be used in conjunction with [its contr.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Har~N","text_ar":"حَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for the sake of assimilation, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qir~N","text_ar":"قِرٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Kt,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cold; coldness; chill; chilness; coolness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barodN","text_ar":"بَرْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Mgh, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qir~apN","text_ar":"قِرَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qur~N","text_ar":"قُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cold;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in winter;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) whereas"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barodN","text_ar":"بَرْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in winter and summer: (M:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qir~apN","text_ar":"قِرَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cold,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by which a man"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other creature,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is affected,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smitten."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daxaluwA fiY Alqur~i","text_ar":"دَخَلُوا فِى القُرِّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They entered upon the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cold."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA Har~a walaA qar~a","text_ar":"لَا حَرَّ وَلَا قَرَّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Neither heat nor cold."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, from a trad.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu qir~apK","text_ar":"ذَاتُ قِرَّةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A night of cold."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$d~u","text_ar":"اشدُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaTa$i Hir~apN EalaY qir~apN","text_ar":"العَطَشِ حِرَّةٌ عَلَى قِرَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The most severe of thirst is thirst in a cold day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hr","text_ar":"حر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And sometimes the Arabs said ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajidu Hir~apN taHota qir~apN","text_ar":"اَجِدُ حِرَّةٌ تَحْتَ قِرَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I experience"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thirst in a cold day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, in TA, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hr","text_ar":"حر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [See this and other exs. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hr","text_ar":"حر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) One says also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahabato qir~atuhaA","text_ar":"ذَهَبَتْ قِرَّتُهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qir~apN","text_ar":"قِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEil~api","text_ar":"العِلَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The time of its access,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coming,"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the access,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coming, of the disease,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the shivering-fit"},{"kind":"text","text":"of an ague, (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurawaA='u","text_ar":"عُرَوَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"departed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the [pronoun]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hA","text_ar":"ها"},{"kind":"text","text":"refers to [the word]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEil~ap","text_ar":"العِلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","K","TA","Mgh","Msb","Lh","Kt"]},{"entry_id":"n35346","headword_ar":"قِرٌّ","root":"qr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qur~N","text_ar":"قُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"page_break","n":2501}],"source_refs":[]}]}}